      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation must be directly linked to the clinical decision endpoint of worst-case hemolysis identification.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) and scalar shear stress exposure time are the primary QoIs, directly corresponding to the regulatory endpoint for hemolysis risk in CPB devices per ISO 10993-4 and FDA guidance."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
