      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sample characterization sufficient to confirm fluid properties; formal statistical sample analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood samples characterized for hematocrit (40±2%), viscosity, and osmolality prior to each test. Inter-sample variability acknowledged in output comparison uncertainty. Formal statistical sample analysis scoped out at MRL 2."
