    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts and the simulation evidence supports the regulatory submission decision. Assessment accepted by unanimous panel review.",
